{"tid":2373032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【中国疫苗？】港區人大政協周五獲安排 到深圳接種新冠疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-20T07:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T07:27:44.000Z","uid":293677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06cdc9d4151eb13408a27bfb1382c5a6803506ac","tid":2373032,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>港區人大政協周五獲安排到深圳接種新冠疫苗</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n最後更新時間 20.01.2021 14:32<br />\n<br />\n 有港區人大和政協下午到灣仔友好協進會會址，接受新型冠狀病毒檢測，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">有政協透露，他們周五會獲安排到深圳接種新冠疫苗。</span></span> 政協委員施榮懷表示，港府目前未批准新冠疫苗在香港使用，因此港區人大和政協要到內地接種疫苗，估計是為3月舉辦的兩會會議做準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2375559&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Iaw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=3e11794d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375559</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">身為中国人 唔係唔打中国疫苗呀話？</span></span>"},{"pid":"37309e92099bc0778c7cb24f5b2e5a0c00271407","tid":2373032,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭同啲司局長<br />\n<br />\n仲有班政府AO呢"},{"pid":"81d8f69b9c02f40f9bae002e74db737f9e9c3ab9","tid":2373032,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"邊個唔去開會就知邊個醒目共狗冇打到傻仔針<br />\n係時候拎份人名表出黎逐個對人名"},{"pid":"d78df1278189015d38d7f81fdde4fe117768ba7a","tid":2373032,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d8f69b9c02f40f9bae002e74db737f9e9c3ab9","tid":2373032,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"邊個唔去開會就知邊個醒目共狗冇打到傻仔針<br />\n係時候拎份人名表出黎逐個對人名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=